'''Troy Resources''' is an Australian mining corporation. It is publicly listed on the [[Australian Securities Exchange]].

==History==
The corporation was established in 1984.<ref name="history">[http://www.troyres.com.au/corporate/history.html Official website: History]</ref> It has been listed on the [[Australian Stock Exchange]] since 1987.<ref name="history"/> It started production and shortly after exploration in [[Southern Cross, Western Australia]].<ref name="history"/>

It operates a mine in [[Andorinhas]] in [[Par√°|Para State]], [[Brazil]] and [[Casposo]] in [[San Juan Province, Argentina|San Juan Province]], [[Argentina]].<ref name="troyresources">[http://www.troyres.com.au/ Official website: Main page]</ref> Additionally, it has a project in [[Guyana]].<ref name="troyresources"/>

On July 12, 2013, it acquired [[Azimuth Resources]].<ref name="troyresources"/>

It operates the [[Sandstone Gold Mine]] in [[Sandstone, Western Australia]]. Ref?

